* MIXED COBOL PROGRAM
* Exercises all token categories together.
 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
 PROGRAM-ID. PAYROLL.
 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
 DATA DIVISION.
 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
 01 EMPLOYEE-ID.
 01 EMPLOYEE-NAME.
 01 SALARY.
 01 TAX-RATE.
 01 NET-PAY.
 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
 MAIN-PARA.
*> Compute net pay
     ACCEPT EMPLOYEE-ID.
     ACCEPT EMPLOYEE-NAME.
     MOVE 50000 TO SALARY.
     MOVE 30 TO TAX-RATE.
     COMPUTE NET-PAY = SALARY - TAX-RATE.
     IF NET-PAY > 0
         DISPLAY "NET PAY: ".
         DISPLAY NET-PAY.
     ELSE
         DISPLAY "NO PAY".
     END-IF.
     PERFORM REPORT-PARA.
     STOP RUN.
 REPORT-PARA.
     DISPLAY "REPORT COMPLETE".
